You need to follow some of the steps to run the program 

First : Creating specific Directory

in Terminal type these commands : -  
mkdir openai_chatbot
cd openai_chatbot

Create templates directory : - 
mkdir templates

Then  CREATE NECESSARY  files : - 
touch app.py basicmodel.py requirements.txt
touch templates/template.html

Add content to each file by pasting the code given in the git repo : - 

Running the Code : - 

Create a virtual environment for running the code : - 
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate 
# On Windows use `venv\Scripts\activate`

Install the required dependecies ; - 
pip install -r requirements.txt

For running the flask application you need to write the following commands : -
python app.py














